{
  "stem": "22840.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The Wehrmacht were just patrols.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were just soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But there were-- there were other things there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The-- in-- in-- in one instance, the Germans burned a house on all the inhabitants because partisans fired from the house, killed three-- three doctors, three German doctors which were walking up-- up this little mountain.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a gun that the-- large gun, that the partisans-- that was left by the Slovak retreating army, by the Slovak in the Slovak uprising, and the partisans used it to shell the Germans.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And it was just standing there, and I remembered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "When I came back, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was no road leading up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The house was exactly where it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "There was a plaque on the house where people were executed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I have the plaque picture, so I remember that correctly, but there was no gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I knew exactly where to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We-- we drove the car, and we came-- we came straight to the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I identified the house, and I told my wife ahead of time how the windows will look, and they looked the same.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we discovered this-- this old lady-- 80 years old lady by the name of Maria Baluhova, which recalled the family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She gave me the names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She recalled me living there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And her mother kept another Jewish woman with her child there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was bothered that I remembered everything, but the road was not there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I thought that the Slovaks will have the-- the-- the sense of leaving the old gun there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It was in the middle of a-- of a beautiful meadow, and it was just absolutely the most reasonable place for a memorial.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
